rox. 1 lg. head)","1 romaine lettuce head, to serve, torn into pieces (approx. 1 lg. head)","2 tomatoes, cored, seeded and diced (¼ in.), (approx. 9 oz)","2 avocados, diced (½ in.), (approx. 12 oz)","blue cheese, crumbled, to serve (approx. 4 oz)","fresh chives, to serve, sliced (¼ in.), (approx. ½ oz)"]}],"id":"r254119","imageLink":"https:\/\/4.bp.blogspot.com\/-Ya2ks0pEDyU\/XZMt7zxuvuI\/AAAAAAAAZ_M\/2Z5i9cp9a9wLXyT0IOTrBycjddGB7TO5ACLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_4H9jKxGz9gV1TrMr.png","title":"Cobb Salad","publishedAt":"2017-10-06T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"30 g","fat":"37 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"10 g","calories":"2054 kJ \/ 491 kcal"},"usefulItems":"pitcher, serving platter","hintsAndTricks":["Make sure steam can circulate when placing chicken in the Varoma. Ensure some holes remain unobstructed for steam to circulate and allow for even cooking."],"basicInfo":["medium","15m","1h","6 portions"]}